<p align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span style='font-family:Times'>Weeks
5 and 6 � Cognitive Theories and Models � exact dates TBD<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p><span style='font-family:Times'>Different theories seek to explain and model
aspects of people�s behavior with systems and, in general, when designing
artifacts. Some of these include construction-integration model, the
human-information processor model, and GOMS/CPM.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

