<p align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span style='font-family:Times'>Weeks7
and 8 � Evaluation � exact dates TBD<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p><span style='font-family:Times'>Experimental methods adapted from cognitive
psychology, anthropology, linguistics, and other human sciences will be
discussed from the perspective of how they can guide the design and evaluate
the implementation of systems.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

